They soar high up in the sky.

1356
02:13:16,299 --> 02:13:18,290
l'm taking Arjun with me.

1357
02:13:18,568 --> 02:13:20,297
lf l leave him here he will become

1358
02:13:20,570 --> 02:13:22,367
another version of you.

1359
02:13:22,706 --> 02:13:26,574
One of you is enough for this world.

1360
02:13:27,310 --> 02:13:31,713
You will never
understand why this happened.

1361
02:13:32,449 --> 02:13:38,854
Because it's a word you've
never known or experienced...

1362
02:13:39,789 --> 02:13:40,847
Love.

1363
02:13:42,058 --> 02:13:46,324
Please don't try to find us. lf you
come within a 100 kilometers of us,

1364
02:13:46,530 --> 02:13:49,522
The police will know you beat Arjun.

1365
02:13:49,933 --> 02:13:53,334
Legally, it's a criminal offence.

1366
02:13:54,337 --> 02:13:57,329
Arjun can be a lot
more than just your slave.

1367
02:13:57,674 --> 02:14:00,336
He needs a family, not a cage.

1368
02:14:00,744 --> 02:14:04,805
He needs a future, which l will make
sure he gets, whatever the cost...

1369
02:14:05,482 --> 02:14:09,748
Congratulations on your new wife,
your new daughter, your new life.

1370
02:14:10,353 --> 02:14:12,412
Your son, Rohan.

1371
02:14:13,423 --> 02:14:22,559
ls life over?. Or is
it about to begin?

1372
02:14:23,700 --> 02:14:32,369
ls this nightfall?
Or is it a new dawn?

1373
02:14:32,776 --> 02:14:38,373
Will the future bring comfort?

1374
02:14:41,718 --> 02:14:48,783
Or will bring us to a crossroad?

1375
02:14:50,794 --> 02:14:58,724
Who knows what lies ahead...